The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically rain removal in images/videos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves atmospheric scattering principles, which falls under the category of computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of deep learning suggests the possibility of machine learning (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and learning theory (cs.LG) categories.
